What is a disk image?
a virtual copy of a disk.
What is the command to make a disk image?
you can use dd to create the file before using cfdisk to format it as a disk image
What is a disk partition?
A localized portion of a hard drive
How many disk partitions are in a disk image?
that depends on how many times the hard drive the image is taken from was partitioned
What difficulties does this pose if any?
you may have difficulties finding specific portions since you cant look across everything at once
What steps must you take to work with this?
you use kpartx before mounting
